items.name: Fusou (Kancolle)
items.description:
An experimental character LoRA of Fusou from Kantai Collection.

Info

Training with 89 images
Followed the manual form [ [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free ],
You can access to this guide in Suggested Resources section.

Recommended set up

Sampler: Euler a, DPM family series
Sampling steps: 20 or 25+
CFG Scale: 7
CLIP Skip: 2
*Do not use [restore face] on anime character!*

LoRA Weighting: [1 - 0.8], (1 - 0.6)

Baking Step:
0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

Upscaler for [Step 1 - 3]: [R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp]
I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

Basic prompts

FusouKC , (FusouKC) japanese clothes, (red) hakama short skirt, (white) socks, tabi

Special outfits

FusouBikiniKC, (one-piece) swimsuit, sandals

-(hair) flower, (floral print) sarong, (flower) scrunchie
-(white) one-piece swimsuit, (casual) one-piece swimsuit
-bare shoulders, (covered) navel, collarbone, cleavage
-barefoot

Some additional tags that you may use for reference

-(white) headband, (FusouKC) hair ornament, headgear, (ribbon) scrunchie
-(FusouKC) nontraditional miko, (detached sleeves) nontraditional miko, (floral print) nontraditional miko
-sash, obi, petals
-bare shoulders, wide sleeves

-red eyes

H. R. Giger art style lora for SDXL 1.0. H. R. Giger is a dark surrealist artist and now you can generate art similar to his style within your own Stable Diffusion workflow. This model was trained on 1024 x 1024 resolution and is able to produce higher details than if you were to simply put his name into your prompt.

Character Lora of SHODAN from System Shock Game Series

"Look at you, hacker: a pathetic creature of meat and bone, panting and sweating as you run through my corridors. How can you challenge a perfect, immortal machine?" -SHODAN

NOTE: Very experimental, cause you know she didn't have any facial features, or hair, or body, or even physically exist, just a bunch of evil pixels. So AI will run wild. -soul3142


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Ko-fi or Patreon.

Main Trigger Word - shodanSS_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

Use LoRA name according to the downloaded file when copying example prompts.

  1. Highres Fix : Use if you are getting blurry and ugly images & try reducing LoRA weight

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.55 - 0.7

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising : Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's : use ADetailer

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

items.name: Discogirl
items.description:
SDXL-lora version of the discomix model.SDXL-lora 版本的 discomix 模型。

Please note that this version is a beta version and I can't guarantee how well it will be generated 请注意，此版本为测试版，我无法保证它的生成效果。

Please use with SDXL1.0

请与 SDXL1.0 搭配使用

Its main image effects are Nightscape, City, Street, Crowd and Discogirl.

它的主要图像效果有夜景、城市、街道、人群和 Discogirl。

Since sdxl is trained with 1024*1024 resolution images compared to sd1.5's 512*512, I chose to adjust the dim to 256 for training, so the size of this lora is 1.7G.

与 sd1.5 的 512*512 相比，sdxl 是用 1024*1024 分辨率的图像进行训练的，因此我选择将训练时的 dim 调整为 256，所以这个 lora 的大小为 1.7G。

Recommended lora weight (0.7~1), 0.7 or less lora's influence will be reduced a lot.

建议的 lora 权重（0.7~1），0.7 或更小的 lora 权重会大大降低影响。

The generated image resolution is recommended to be above 1024*1024.

生成图像的分辨率建议在 1024*1024 以上。

Negative prompt：(worst quality, low quality:1.4),nsfw,(hand with more than 5 fingers, hand with less than 4 fingers,ad anatomy, bad hands,mutated hands and fingers:1.2),extra legs,extra arms,interlocked fingers,duplicate,cropped,text,jpeg artifacts,signature,watermark,username,blurry,artist name,trademark,title,muscular,sd character,multiple view,Reference sheet,long body,malformed limbs,multiple breasts,cloned face,malformed,mutated,bad anatomy,disfigured,bad proportions,duplicate,bad feet,artist name,extra limbs,ugly,fused anus,text font ui,missing limb,

items.name: Action SDXL
items.description:
Tired of boring images and can't be bothered to use controlnet? Use this LoRA and it will add dynamic poses, action camera angles and lots of energy and movement to your images.

Follow me to make sure you see new tools like this, or new styles, poses and Nobodys when I post them. More Clutter series coming too. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

How to use:
Works at full strength, not overtrained. Use the trigger word zdyna_pose in the positive prompt. Some other useful keywords are posing in zdyna_pose, dutch angle, foreshortening, motion blur, from above, from below, blurred foreground.

Preview Images:
Were generated using ComfyUI and/or InvokeAI. Special thanks to EDG for technical advice in training this concept.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi

items.name: Dannar Toxico - トキシッコ・ダナー
items.description:
Dannar Toxico

Recommended to use at 0.6 to 0.8

Some other words can help like... black hair, blue eyes, blush, hair bobbles, hair ornaments,

These are rarely required but were present during training.

black legwear, capelet, dress, long sleeves, pantyhose, staff,twintails

I used automatic booru tag so the there was also a couple of useless words included during the training but it dont seem to impact the final result that much. The traing data were almost all image with the same outfit. So unless specifying something else she will wear the purple and black mage outfit by default.
